(Republished)

In the Matter of 32 West 32nd Street Corporation, Appellant. Jacob Reiser et al., Respondents.

Final order dismissing petition unanimously reversed, with costs to the appellant, and the landlord-petitioner-appellant’s application granted to the extent of fixing the rent at $952.20 per annum. (See Matter of Rutherford Estates [Dorman Products], 277 App. Div. 1.) No opinion. Settle order on notice. Present — Peek, P. J., Glennon, Dore, Yan Yoorhis and Shientag, JJ. [See ante, p. 980.]
